        <code>10.0.8.1-10.0.8.9</code>.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th>DNS</th>
        <td>Enter <code>168.63.129.16</code>.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th>Gateway</th>
        <td>Enter the first IP address of the subnet. For example, <code>10.0.8.1</code>.</td>
